citations:
    citation-acok-sansa-viii:
        source: source-acok
        properties:
            locator: "Sansa VIII"
            text_from_source: "It's done! Done! Done! The city is saved. Lord Stannis is dead, Lord Stannis is fled, no one knows, no one cares, his host is broken, the danger's done. Slaughtered, scattered, or gone over, they say."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Aftermath of the Battle of the Blackwater from Sansa's POV. Sandor Clegane deserts and confronts Sansa in her bedchamber before fleeing the city. Dontos brings news of the victory — Tywin Lannister and the Tyrells arrived and routed Stannis from the rear. The vanguard was led under the banner of 'Lord Renly' (actually Garlan Tyrell wearing Renly's armor). Stannis fled."
